text: Bandaru Dattatreya (born 12 June 1947) is an Indian politician. In September 2019, he became the Governor of the State of Himachal Pradesh. He was the Member of Lok Sabha for Secunderabad since 2014. He is a member of the Bharatiya Janata Party (BJP). ==References== Category:1947 births Category:Living people Category:Governors of Himachal Pradesh Category:Governors of Haryana Category:Members of the Lok Sabha
